HEADWORD: Leptoptilus
<hw>Leptoptilus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A genus of birds including the
adjutant bird (<spn>Leptoptilus dubius</spn>, also called adjutant
stork) and marabous.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Leptoptilus</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
